for fixing freezing problem of ubuntu(like rishi and saish)
--> press E on grub loader
--> then add nomodeset to last second line to start it
for SSD laptop
--> sudo nano /etc/default/grub
-->change this to GRUB_CMDLINE_LINUX_DEFAULT="quiet splash nomodeset"
--> then one link is there to install drivers(rishi whatsapp follow that)
